OL,3,COfcom fines Royal Mail #10.5m for post
OL,4,Cmissing delivery targets
OL,6,FThe post office regulator has issued a
OL,7,Frecord-high fine on Royal Mail for
OL,8,Fmissing targets on first and second
OL,9,Fclass deliveries, ITV News' reporter
OL,10,FCaroline Lewis explains
OL,12,FRegulator Ofcom has fined Royal Mail
OL,13,F#10.5 million for missing its post
OL,14,Fdelivery targets in the 2023-2024
OL,15,Ffinancial year.
OL,17,FThe fine is the second in two years,
OL,18,Fafter the watchdog also gave Royal
OL,19,FMail a #5.6 million penalty in
OL,20,FNovember 2023.
