OL,3,COfcom fines Royal Mail #10.5m for post
OL,4,Cmissing delivery targets
OL,6,FRoyal Mail said just under three-
OL,7,Fquarters of first class post was
OL,8,Fdelivered on time during the period,
OL,9,Fwell short of its 93% target.
OL,11,FAnd 92.7% of second class post was
OL,12,Fdelivered on time, below its 98.5%
OL,13,Ftarget, it said.
OL,15,FIan Strawhorne, Ofcom director of
OL,16,Fenforcement, said: "With millions of
OL,17,Fletters arriving late, far too many
OL,18,Fpeople aren't getting what they pay
OL,19,Ffor when they buy a stamp.
