OL,6,F"Royal Mail's poor service is now
OL,7,Feroding public trust in one of the
OL,8,FUK's oldest institutions.
OL,10,F"This is the second time we've fined
OL,11,Fthe company since the pandemic.
OL,13,F"Royal Mail has provided an
OL,14,Fimprovement plan, and we're seeing
OL,15,Fsome signs of progress, but it must go
OL,16,Ffurther and faster to deliver the
OL,17,Fservice that people expect."
