OL,3,COfcom fines Royal Mail #10.5m for post
OL,4,Cmissing delivery targets
OL,6,FThe universal service currently
OL,7,Frequires Royal Mail to deliver letters
OL,8,Fsix days a week and parcels five days
OL,9,Fa week, but is under review.
OL,11,FThe fine comes as Czech billionaire
OL,12,FDaniel Kretinsky closes in on a deal
OL,13,Fto buy Royal Mail from current owner
OL,14,FInternational Distribution Services.
OL,16,FDaniel Kretinsky's EP Group agreed to
OL,17,Fbuy IDS earlier this year, but is
OL,18,Fbelieved to have agreed to several
OL,19,Fconcessions to gain approval.
