OL,6,FHe had already guaranteed to maintain
OL,7,Fthe universal service.
OL,9,FMr Kretinsky has also pledged not to
OL,10,Fraid the group's pension surplus, and
OL,11,Fkeep the brand name and Royal Mail's
OL,12,FUK tax residency and headquarters.
OL,14,FThere was also an agreement to respect
OL,15,Funion demand for no compulsory
OL,16,Fredundancies until 2025.
OL,18,FIt is thought some of these
OL,19,Fsafeguards, such as the commitment to
OL,20,Favoid compulsory redundancies, could
OL,21,Fbe extended as part of a new agreement.
